{"tid":666342,"cid":35,"subCid":0,"title":"仲有8個月搬, 但寬頻呢個月到期","createTime":"2018-05-15T19:44:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-24T10:02:49.000Z","uid":85056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a484b2d4cc1f608b2f26ba8fbbbf6b96ccc1b3e6","tid":666342,"uid":85056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T19:44:26.000Z","msg":"一直用HKBN上網100MB連電話<br />\n月底完約, 本來下個月搬新地方所以交左cut form<br />\n淨係每個月$30留返個電話 (個號碼唔帶走要俾屋企人)<br />\n點知有D事要押後搬屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 至少8個月<br />\n之前同HKBN個sale講個情況<br />\n佢話我搬可以帶埋個plan走<br />\n但個電話號碼都要帶走埋<br />\n新地方個號碼要再申請過再簽約, 另加上網安裝費<br />\n咁我新地方即係帶住個 上網+舊號碼 合約<br />\n另外再加新號碼合約?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我話考慮下先再覆佢<br />\n有冇sale有好建議，轉台都得<br />\n1) 舊電話要留喺而家個地方<br />\n2) 新地方想要上網100/500MB+電話 (新號碼)<br />\n解決到短時間內即簽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22ec08ccb797b3f0af983706c8f82f51f229796b","tid":666342,"uid":85056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T00:49:03.000Z","msg":"係咪冇短期既寛頻合約<br />\n諗緊係咪要買部4G router 頂住先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0705d8691ffe5901e1cad5e4ee983b13fe829f74","tid":666342,"uid":174094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T06:26:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9eda95fe322124a79fff52948591f59bf722479c","tid":666342,"uid":175521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T06:27:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3ae991db4e3f2b74e01bad8f359bda1e0235ad92","tid":666342,"uid":183573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T07:39:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f0b664e4d33b00efe993d7b30dda57176bef44dd","tid":666342,"uid":50895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T05:17:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"64d6e30b00e07b7a2077a3595b759f